{% extends 'headers/header.html.twig' %}
{% block tag_title %} Bienvenue - Hypnos {% endblock %}
{% block title %} Accueil Hypnos {% endblock %}
{% block main%}

    <div class="card text-white border-0">
        <img src="{{ img }}" class="card-img-fluid" alt="...">
        <div class="card-img-overlay ">
            <div class="position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle">
                <h1 class="card-title text-center">LES MEILLEURS HOTELS DE L'HEXAGONE</h1>
                <p class="card-text text-center">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <main class="container-fluid" style="background-color: whitesmoke">
        <div>
            <p><b>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean non purus ac tortor accumsan malesuada vel vitae augue. Suspendisse lobortis elit a ante facilisis dapibus. Praesent odio leo, finibus at posuere sit amet, varius sit amet ex. Curabitur ultricies at ipsum ac sodales. Nunc aliquam, lorem eu aliquam laoreet, enim purus placerat magna, eu semper urna eros quis orci. Nunc sed nisi id ipsum pharetra bibendum.</b></p>
        </div>

        {% for article in articles %}
            <div class="card mb-3 d-flex justify-content-center"style="max-width:800px">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <img src="{{ article.image }}" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">{{ article.title }}</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">{{ article.content }}</p>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}

        <div class="row mb-2 justify-content-center">
            <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aQIaW7fBYxw" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>

    </main>
{% endblock main %}
